# skill: handoff-prepare
# purpose: Prepare work for handoff between agents/personas
# triggers: Agent needs to pass work to another

## Invocation
```
handoff-prepare <task-id> --from <source-agent> --to <target-agent> \
    [--notes <handoff-notes>]
```

## Output
Creates: `memory/tasks/<task-id>/handoff.md`

## Implementation Flow

### 1. Gather State
```bash
#!/bin/bash
# handoff-prepare.skill implementation

TASK_ID="$1"
FROM_AGENT="$2"
TO_AGENT="$3"
NOTES="${4:-}"

# Gather all artifacts
TASK=$(cat "memory/tasks/$TASK_ID/input.json" 2>/dev/null)
CURRENT_PHASE=$(cat "memory/tasks/$TASK_ID/.current_phase" 2>/dev/null)
```

### 2. Generate Handoff Document
```markdown
# Handoff: {{task_id}}

## Handoff Details
**From:** {{from_agent}}
**To:** {{to_agent}}
**Date:** {{date}}
**Task:** {{task_id}}

## Current State

### Task Summary
$(cat "memory/tasks/$TASK_ID/input.json" | jq -r '.description')

### Completed Work
$(git log --oneline --grep="\[$TASK_ID\]" | head -10)

### Artifacts Created
$(find memory/tasks/$TASK_ID -type f -name "*.md" | sed 's/memory\/tasks\//  - /')

### Checkpoints
$(git log --oneline --all | grep "\[$TASK_ID\]" | head -20)

## What's Done
| Phase | Status | Notes |
|-------|--------|---|
| Review | ✓ | |
| Plan | ✓ | |
| Outline | ✓ | |
| Locate | ✓ | |
| Execute | ✓/✗ | |
| Ship | ✓/✗ | |

## What's Next
$(cat "memory/tasks/$TASK_ID/.next_steps" 2>/dev/null || "See task context")

## Pending Items
| Item | Priority | Blocker |
|------|---|---|
| <item> | H/M/L | <yes/no> |

## Context Notes
$(if [ -n "$NOTES" ]; then
    echo "$NOTES"
else
    echo "No additional notes"
fi)

## Known Issues
| Issue | Impact | Mitigation |
|-------|--------|---|
| <issue> | H/M/L | <mitigation> |

## Dependencies
| Dependency | Status |
|---|---|
| <dependency> | ✓/✗ |

## Files Modified
$(git diff --name-only HEAD~5 | head -20)

## Environment
- Working branch: $(git branch --show-current)
- Last commit: $(git log -1 --oneline)
- Working directory: $(pwd)

## Action Required
- [ ] Review handoff document
- [ ] Check all artifacts
- [ ] Address known issues
- [ ] Continue with next phase

## Contact
Questions? Reference:
- Task: memory/tasks/$TASK_ID/
- Design: memory/designs/$TASK_ID/ (if exists)
- Git history: git log --all --grep="$TASK_ID"
```

### 3. Create Handoff Record
```bash
mkdir -p "memory/personas/$TO_AGENT/handoffs"
cp "memory/tasks/$TASK_ID/handoff.md" "memory/personas/$TO_AGENT/handoffs/$TASK_ID.md"

# Update task state
echo "$TO_AGENT" > "memory/tasks/$TASK_ID/.assigned_to"
echo "$(date -Iseconds)" > "memory/tasks/$TASK_ID/.handoff_at"
```

### 4. Checkpoint
```bash
checkpoint --phase custom --description "Handoff prepared: $TASK_ID from $FROM_AGENT to $TO_AGENT" \
    --next "$TO_AGENT resumes work"
```
